files that are present in the workspace but not yet in git. Untracked files are
listed by name only (no diff body). If they are machine-local artifacts, use
`add_to_git_exclude` so the user-level exclude stops tracking them locally. If
they are actual binary or generated artifacts that should never enter the repo,
